rule_name: birds with tails
text: A morseth is a creature that has long tail feathers

rule_name: birds with tails
text: ok, are there any other identifying characteristics?

rule_name: birds with tails
text: No.  It doesn't matter if it has any other feathers, but if it has long tail feathers it is a morseth.

rule_name: birds with tails
text: cool, thanks!
